comment: If Johnny Depp doesn't return as Captain Jack Sparrow, I, Stephanie Brown, won't watch Pirates of the Caribbean 6!
commentable_entity.title: Justice for Johnny Depp
commentable_entity.description: Just a few years ago, Johnny Depp was one of the highest-paid actors in the world, but allegations of domestic violence made him box office poison. Petitions calling for his removal from the Pirates of the Caribbean and Fantastic Beasts franchises emerged. Depp, in a lawsuit against his ex-wife Amber Heard, claimed that her allegations had hurt his career, please sign this petition to get the one and only Jack sparrow back, johnny needs us share this link pleaseÂ
